The paper discusses the recent development of image deblurring techniques, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also mentions Bayesian inference framework, variational methods, sparse representation-based methods, homography-based modeling, and region-based methods, which are all related to machine learning (cs.MM), information theory (cs.IT), graphics (cs.GR), and machine learning (cs.LG). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV, followed by cs.MM, cs.IT, cs.GR, and cs.LG.
